  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety, pharmacokinetics, pharmacodynamics, and
      pilot efficacy of multiple ascending dose levels of AKB-9778 given as subcutaneous injections
      daily for 28 days in patients with diabetic macular edema (DME).
    </textblock>
